#### Playbook de Ansible:

### Ejemplo de Playbook de Ansible para GNS3 Server v3.0.0rc1 (sin `pip`)

```yaml
---
- name: Instalar GNS3 Server v3.0.0rc1
  hosts: gns3_servers
  become: yes
  tasks:
    - name: Instalar dependencias necesarias
      apt:
        name:
          - python3
          - python3-dev
          - git
          - wget
          - unzip
          - python3-pyqt5
          - python3-pyqt5.qtsvg
          - python3-pyqt5.qtwebkit
        state: present

    - name: Descargar GNS3 Server v3.0.0rc1
      get_url:
        url: https://github.com/GNS3/gns3-server/archive/refs/tags/v3.0.0rc1.tar.gz
        dest: /opt/gns3-server.tar.gz

    - name: Descomprimir GNS3 Server
      unarchive:
        src: /opt/gns3-server.tar.gz
        dest: /opt/
        remote_src: yes

    - name: Crear un enlace simb√≥lico para gns3server
      command: ln -s /opt/gns3-server-3.0.0rc1/gns3server /usr/local/bin/gns3server
      args:
        removes: /usr/local/bin/gns3server

    - name: Iniciar GNS3 Server
      command: /usr/local/bin/gns3server
      async: 1
      poll: 0
```
